<title>
Countershaft Assembly Disassembly and Reassembly
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B5106037">A/T Assembly Disassembly</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B5106064">A/T Assembly Reassembly</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B5106054">Countershaft Assembly Components</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B5106055001">
<title>
Disassembly
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove countershaft left bearing (1) and reduction driven gear (2) together using special tool and hydraulic press.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5A033">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09925-98221">
09925–98221
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I7V10A510080.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "57.647mm" ver = "01" gw = "102" gh = "146"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<c-change/>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove countershaft right bearing (1) using special tools.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5A034">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09913-61510">
09913–61510
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5A035">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09926-58010">
09926–58010
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B510211.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.746mm" ver = "01" gw = "100" gh = "127"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B5106055002">
<title>
Reassembly
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Press-fit new countershaft right bearing (1) using special tool and hydraulic press.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Replace countershaft right bearing together with bearing cup as a set.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5A036">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09913-84510">
09913–84510
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B510212.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "52.948mm" ver = "01" gw = "62" gh = "133"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Press-fit reduction driven gear (1) using special tools and hydraulic press.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5A037">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09913-84510">
09913–84510
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5A038">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09925-88210">
09925–88210
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B510213.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "48.206mm" ver = "01" gw = "79" gh = "120"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Press-fit countershaft left bearing (1) using special tools and hydraulic press.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5A039">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09913-84510">
09913–84510
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5A040">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09925-88210">
09925–88210
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B510214.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "52.270mm" ver = "01" gw = "80" gh = "131"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
